  <!-- WHY NYAYA-SETU -->
  <section class="ns-why">
    <div class="ns-why-inner">
      <div class="ns-why-header">
        <span class="ns-about-label">THE PROBLEM</span>
        <h2 class="ns-about-sec-title">INDIA'S TRUST DEFICIT IN DIGITAL EVIDENCE</h2>
        <p class="ns-about-sec-desc">A broken chain of custody is costing justice — here's why it must change.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ns-why-grid">

        <div class="ns-why-card">
          <div class="ns-why-icon ns-why-icon--danger">
            <svg width="26" height="26" fill="none" stroke="var(--danger)" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/>
              <line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="ns-why-title">Single Point of Failure</h3>
          <p class="ns-why-desc">Traditional centralized servers can be breached. Corrupt insiders can swap or delete evidence files before trial — with zero trace and zero accountability.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="ns-why-card">
          <div class="ns-why-icon ns-why-icon--danger">
            <svg width="26" height="26" fill="none" stroke="var(--danger)" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
              <line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="ns-why-title">1–30% Conviction Rate</h3>
          <p class="ns-why-desc">NCRB data shows cybercrime convictions hover at a staggering 1–30% in major cities — primarily because digital evidence gets successfully challenged or deemed inadmissible in court.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="ns-why-card">
          <div class="ns-why-icon ns-why-icon--danger">
            <svg width="26" height="26" fill="none" stroke="var(--danger)" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/>
              <line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/>
              <line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="ns-why-title">2+ Year FSL Backlog</h3>
          <p class="ns-why-desc">Forensic Science Labs are overwhelmed with routine authentication tasks, causing multi-year delays that keep undertrials in jail long before any verdict is reached.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- NEW: Corruption card -->
        <div class="ns-why-card ns-why-card--corrupt">
          <div class="ns-why-icon ns-why-icon--corrupt">
            <svg width="26" height="26" fill="none" stroke="#f59e0b" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <circle cx="12" cy="8" r="3"/>
              <path d="M6.5 20h11l-1.5-6H8L6.5 20z"/>
              <path d="M12 11v3M9 14h6"/>
              <path d="M3 9l2-2M21 9l-2-2M3 15l2 2M21 15l-2 2"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="ns-why-title ns-why-title--corrupt">Money Can't Buy Truth</h3>
          <p class="ns-why-desc">Wealthy accused can <em class="corrupt-em">bribe officers to swap files</em>, <em class="corrupt-em">pressure judges</em>, or pay to have evidence quietly deleted from central servers before trial. Human honesty is not a security model.</p>
          <div class="ns-why-corrupt-tag">
            <svg width="12" height="12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
            Blockchain removes this attack vector entirely
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ns-why-card">
          <div class="ns-why-icon ns-why-icon--danger">
            <svg width="26" height="26" fill="none" stroke="var(--danger)" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"/>
              <polyline points="3.27 6.96 12 12.01 20.73 6.96"/><line x1="12" y1="22.08" x2="12" y2="12"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="ns-why-title">The Deepfake Threat</h3>
          <p class="ns-why-desc">With AI tools, fabricating convincing video or audio evidence is now trivial. We need a way to prove a file hasn't changed by even one byte since the moment of seizure.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="ns-why-card ns-why-card--solution">
          <div class="ns-why-icon ns-why-icon--gr">
            <svg width="26" height="26" fill="none" stroke="var(--e4)" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
              <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="ns-why-title ns-why-title--gr">Nyaya-Setu Solves This</h3>
          <p class="ns-why-desc">By anchoring every file's SHA-256 hash on the Sepolia blockchain and storing the original on IPFS, we make tampering <em>mathematically impossible</em> — not just policy-restricted.</p>
          <a href="/dashboard" class="ns-why-learn-more">
            Learn how it works
            <svg width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section class="ns-how">
    <div class="ns-how-inner">
      <div class="ns-how-header">
        <span class="ns-about-label">PROTOCOL</span>
        <h2 class="ns-about-sec-title">3-STEP VERIFICATION ENGINE</h2>
        <p class="ns-about-sec-desc">From seizure to court — a mathematically tamper-proof chain of custody.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ns-steps">

        <div class="ns-step">
          <div class="ns-step-num">01</div>
          <div class="ns-step-body">
            <div class="ns-step-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="var(--c4)" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/>
                <polyline points="17 8 12 3 7 8"/>
                <line x1="12" y1="3" x2="12" y2="15"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="ns-step-title">UPLOAD & HASH</h3>
            <p class="ns-step-desc">Officer uploads evidence. System generates SHA-256 fingerprint and pins the file to IPFS via Pinata.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ns-step-arrow">
          <svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="rgba(0,210,230,0.4)" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <div class="ns-step">
          <div class="ns-step-num">02</div>
          <div class="ns-step-body">
            <div class="ns-step-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="var(--c4)" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/>
                <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="ns-step-title">IMMUTABLE SEAL</h3>
            <p class="ns-step-desc">Officer signs via MetaMask. Hash + Case ID written to Solidity smart contract on Sepolia — permanent and timestamped.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ns-step-arrow">
          <svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="rgba(0,210,230,0.4)" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <div class="ns-step">
          <div class="ns-step-num">03</div>
          <div class="ns-step-body">
            <div class="ns-step-icon">
              <svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="var(--e4)" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/>
                <path d="M21 12c0 4.97-4.03 9-9 9s-9-4.03-9-9 4.03-9 9-9 9 4.03 9 9z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="ns-step-title">INSTANT VERIFY</h3>
            <p class="ns-step-desc">Judge uploads file. System recalculates hash and compares with blockchain. Match = admissible. Mismatch = fetch Golden Copy.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div style="text-align:center; margin-top: 2.5rem;">
        <a href="/index" class="ns-cta ns-cta--primary" style="display:inline-flex;">
          <svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 8v4l3 3"/></svg>
          Explore the Full Protocol
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TESTIMONIALS -->
  <section class="ns-testi">
    <div class="ns-testi-inner">
      <div class="ns-how-header">
        <span class="ns-about-label">VOICES</span>
        <h2 class="ns-about-sec-title">WHAT THE SYSTEM ENABLES</h2>
        <p class="ns-about-sec-desc">Perspectives from the four pillars of India's justice ecosystem.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ns-testi-grid">

        <div class="ns-testi-card">
          <div class="ns-testi-quote">"</div>
          <p class="ns-testi-text">Before Nyaya-Setu, we spent weeks preparing Section 65B certificates manually. Now it's generated the moment we upload. Our team can focus on actual investigation.</p>
          <div class="ns-testi-author">
            <div class="ns-testi-avatar ns-testi-avatar--c">
              <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="var(--c4)" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="ns-testi-name">Inspector R. Sharma</div>
              <div class="ns-testi-role">Cyber Crime Unit, Delhi Police</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ns-testi-card">
          <div class="ns-testi-quote">"</div>
          <p class="ns-testi-text">Evidence integrity checks that used to take 3–6 months through the FSL now happen in under a minute. This is the kind of infrastructure the judiciary has been waiting for.</p>
          <div class="ns-testi-author">
            <div class="ns-testi-avatar ns-testi-avatar--g">
              <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="var(--e4)" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 6l9-4 9 4v6c0 5.25-3.75 10.15-9 11.5C6.75 22.15 3 17.25 3 12V6z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="ns-testi-name">Hon. Justice A. Mehta</div>
              <div class="ns-testi-role">Sessions Court, Mumbai</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ns-testi-card">
          <div class="ns-testi-quote">"</div>
          <p class="ns-testi-text">Our lab backlog has always been blamed for delayed justice. With blockchain-anchored hashes, routine authentication is instant — freeing us for complex forensic analysis.</p>
          <div class="ns-testi-author">
            <div class="ns-testi-avatar ns-testi-avatar--c">
              <svg width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="var(--c4)" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M19.07 4.93a10 10 0 0 1 0 14.14M4.93 4.93a10 10 0 0 0 0 14.14"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="ns-testi-name">Dr. P. Nair</div>
              <div class="ns-testi-role">Director, State Forensic Science Lab</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STATS BAR -->
  <section class="ns-threats">
    <div class="ns-threats-inner">
      <div class="ns-threat-card">
        <div class="ns-threat-val">5 CR+</div>
        <div class="ns-threat-lbl">Pending Cases in India</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ns-threat-div"></div>
      <div class="ns-threat-card">
        <div class="ns-threat-val ns-threat-val--danger">1–30%</div>
        <div class="ns-threat-lbl">Cybercrime Conviction Rate</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ns-threat-div"></div>
      <div class="ns-threat-card">
        <div class="ns-threat-val">2+ YRS</div>
        <div class="ns-threat-lbl">Forensic Lab Backlog</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ns-threat-div"></div>
      <div class="ns-threat-card">
        <div class="ns-threat-val ns-threat-val--gr">&lt;₹1</div>
        <div class="ns-threat-lbl">Cost Per Case on Chain</div>
      </div>
    </div>
